<HEADLINE> Indians' Karsay Has Elbow Surgery </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	CLEVELAND (AP) -- Cleveland Indians reliever Steve Karsay had  
arthroscopic surgery on his right elbow, the club said Wednesday. 
</P>
