<HEADLINE> Former First Ladies Honored </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	NEW YORK (AP) -- Former first ladies Barbara Bush, Rosalynn  
Carter, Betty Ford, Lady Bird Johnson and Nancy Reagan have been 
honored for their contributions to health and education. 
