<TEXT>
<P>
 *Celebrity Spotlight &AMP; Birthdays    	

</P>
<P>
	Comedian Dennis Miller has two new HBO projects. ``Dennis  
Miller: The Millennium Special'' will be his fifth solo effort on 
HBO. The one-hour special is scheduled to air on Dec. 4. A new 
season of his Emmy-winning weekly series, ``Dennis Miller Live,'' 
will begin in January. Miller was born on Nov. 3, 1953. 

</P>
