	According to ``Advice to a Son:''  
</P>
<P>
	``Always put paper on the seat,  
</P>
<P>
	``Don't believe in wars,  
</P>
<P>
	``Keep yourself both clean and neat.  
</P>
<P>
	``Never marry whores.''  
  	   	
</P>
